{"tid":189033,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[澳門] HUSH Full Music 沙灘音樂會","createTime":"2017-04-06T06:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T02:51:05.000Z","uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a06279ae4aabe5946e918ad598950444b3f930","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"有無人會去喱個音樂會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間：4月30日及5月1日<br />\n地點：澳門黑沙海灘<br />\n費用：免費入場<br />\nHUSH 官方網頁： <a href=\"http://www.icm.gov.mo/hush\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icm.gov.mo%2Fhush&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=357fcc99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.icm.gov.mo/hush</a><br />\nFacebook Page：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hushfullmusic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhushfullmusic%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7b25dd8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hushfullmusic/</a><br />\n<br />\nLine Up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n<br />\n陳奐仁 / 盧凱彤 / SUPPER MOMENT /<br />\nKINOCO HOTEL / HELLO NICO / MARY SEE THE FUTURE 先知瑪莉 / STREETGUNS /<br />\n野孩子 /六道母 / BREAK THE RULES<br />\n<br />\n恭碩良 / FORGET THE G / WHYOCEANS /<br />\nWAT DE FUNK / SCAMPER / CROSSLINE /<br />\nACHUN / BOMBEIROS / CATALYSER /<br />\nDE-AQUA / FRONTLINE CASTE / HOU + SUMMER /<br />\nSONIA KA IAN LAO + VJ MIGUEL / <br />\n80&amp;TAL / 石裂符ZENITH"},{"pid":"a546e971559b3050f473f2351b107e5e4a057193","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"時間表 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sfuiw82t\" data-thumbnail-s