g":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係你呀老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都幾好心機成日mon呢啲音樂會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得喱啲show真係睇一次少一次 講句唔好聽都唔知仲有無下一次 所以一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我早幾年 <br />\n都成日去呢啲大大小小<br />\n要錢唔洗錢既都去<br />\n<br />\n間唔中就識到啲正band<br />\n最有印象係兩隊日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff8ac725bead3323c732eea84df5d13a2f8060b","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又係你呀老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都幾好心機成日mon呢啲音樂會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得喱啲show真係睇一次少一次 講句唔好聽都唔知仲有無下一次 所以一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我早幾年 <br />\n都成日去呢啲大大小小<br />\n要錢唔洗錢既都去<br />\n<br />\n間唔中就識到啲正band<br />\n最有印象係兩隊日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我宜家就係喱種心態<br />\n一來係因為實在無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但每次去睇都覺得好熱血 又可以識到正band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係澳門朋友話澳門有幾隊band都好正<br />\n所以我就決定過去同佢一齊欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2222abc85b8e7d2ed5c0327024589c32188c1cfe","tid":189033,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n今次係澳門朋友話澳門有幾隊band都好正<br />\n所以我就決定過去同佢一齊欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公道講句, 澳門音樂水平唔差的<br />\n就算一個普通歌手, 歌藝都好過香港歌手"},{"pid":"a97bc7622fb3eb23ae56044d679d3ec03232c58f","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n今次係澳門朋友話澳門有幾隊band都好正<br />\n所以我就決定過去同佢一齊欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公道講句, 澳門音樂水平唔差的<br />\n就算一個普通歌手, 歌藝都好過香港歌手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以過去玩下識多啲band 反正今次免費入場 識完下次有其他show就可以買飛入場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e365745770bf29dbe16f5fa29fad2200a313228","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322c0c254bba25b4ce62ff6183c5266e0120b4c","tid":189033,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:50:57.000Z","msg":"睇 fb page 介紹, <br />\n有d 澳門 Band 幾正"},{"pid":"650f0c566a02da59ef91574ce78c91bfbfd96cc3","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇 fb page 介紹, <br />\n有d 澳門 Band 幾正</blockquote><br />\n係!!! 所以我都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇Scamper"},{"pid":"bca47d072d319a216fe70f09ca29e612d8ed8244","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"最後有無人去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我等到就黎傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6336c494feda4c7760083228fd94ee67c861fcd7","tid":189033,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c272c41888184ab4489054500094bdf20a02cfb","tid":189033,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門黑沙海灘收到香港電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj